title: Kyle Suelflow
text:
Pronouns: he/him Education: Macalester College, B.S. Data Science
Short Bio: My name is Kyle Suelflow, and I am a Junior at Macalester College majoring in Data Science. I am excited to continue to build on my Data Science skills this year. I have been especially keen to learn more about spatial analysis, and spatial visualizations, and am currently working on a project analyzing solar and wind projects in the United States.
